      • parse

        public static AnchoredTextSegment parse(java.lang.String input)
        Attempts to parse a single string as an anchored text segment representation. This is a multiline string with the segment on the first line followed by any number of lines (at least one), representing TextAnchor instances.
        Parameters:
        input - The string to parse
        Returns:
        a new AnchoredTextSegment with at least one TextAnchor or null if the input could not be parsed
